Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I got divorced three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Or to be more precise, my wife left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate,\Nrather than listening to my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,my ears were always focused on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're just a collector\Nwho peeks into people's hearts."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you're not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My work of peeking deep into\Nthe dormant depths of a person's heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,comes with the possibility of\Nfalling deep into those depths myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the fourth victim\Nwas an 18-year-old girl from Munich, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you sexually aroused\Nwhen you chopped her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me about the twelfth victim instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Hanna Kemp of Kropp House.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,52 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-At the time, I--\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably will ask eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but what I want to hear about now\Nis the 11 incidents before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the peak of your sexual arousal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,before or after you commit the murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This tells us all his victims were\Nlong-haired women from 16 to 18 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His crimes clearly fall under\Nthe category of sex murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But he also confessed to a twelfth murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the victim of this case,\NMrs. Kemp,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is at the old age of 52.\NThere are no signs that sex occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He also claims that it was done\Nat the request of a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,thus trying to confuse\Nour investigation… What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudy, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this was\Nthe only way I could see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm a serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell just from newspapers, TV,\Nand rumors from college friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you visit me of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, you looked down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time we made eye contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that you felt contempt toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to\Nrepay my debt from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it money?\N-No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're an authority\Non criminal psychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's something\NI want you to look at for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me. Look at me."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is how big the monster\Ninside me has grown, Dr. Tenma."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Save me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside me\Nis about to burst out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This Johan you speak of is\Nthe true killer of the hospital director,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,killing his foster parents\None after the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving these messages\Nand disappearing once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find him as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to prove your innocence\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost 20 years ago,\Nat a prestigious medical school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a man\Nwho settled for nothing but first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, a Japanese student enrolled\Nand completely changed that man's status.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He was sociable\Nand gained everyone's respect right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He had superior grades to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He easily dragged down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the man at the top of the class\Nduring the midyear exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The man was desperate to take back\Nhis top rank during the final exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He did perfectly\Nin every subject until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, his final test
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,was Introduction to Forensic Medicine,\Nhis worst subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If he failed this,\Neverything would've been for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The man resorted to his final option.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That top rank is mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Japanese man didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the man\Nspectacularly came back on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you can deduce\Nfrom these two messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,About the multiple personalities\Nthat you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that\None personality caused the incident
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other\Nis trying to stop him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are indeed serial murder cases\Nin which such a message is left on scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes, it might be\Na means of running from one's evil deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding the difference\Nis where we psychoanalysts come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people mistakenly assume\Nthat serial killers are introverted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're greatly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Some serial killers are intelligent,\Nsociable, and good at speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're big liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he toying with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hold on,\Nwe shouldn't rush to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me\Nmore about Johan in detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I got divorced three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or to be more precise,\Nmy wife left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an interesting talk, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do\Nsome thorough research on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact me in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm familiar with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me which part?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that he calls
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So there is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It indeed exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside you. Inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's even a monster inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just an armchair theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that monsters\Nreally exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate being looked at with contempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Security…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,\Nthere are scarier things in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you in on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll definitely come to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He will come for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll immediately contact you when he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:10:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to let me use him as\Na research subject after he is arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a very curious criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you in on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Go visit Mrs. Kemp's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The basement storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand if you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There, you will find proof
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that monsters are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd love to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Inspector Kohl? \NI made an appointment with Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight o'clock tonight.\NIn front of the fountain at Oder Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am inspecting the entry route\Ntaken by Jürgens on the day of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,According to his confession, he stayed in\Nthis storage room for several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And right after Mrs. Kemp came home,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he broke into the second floor bedroom\Nand committed his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything looks normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are a lot\Nof framed photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They are photos of Mrs. Kemp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see nothing out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not see any proof of monsters\Nthat Jürgens mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, the twelfth murder\Nwas to confuse us in our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He confessed that this murder\Nwas done at the request of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He also called this friend a monster…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a child,\Nmy mother hit me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a big doll\Nthat my mom treasured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A female doll with long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd wish for that doll to save me\Nduring my beatings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But all it did was grin as it watched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, that storage room\Nwas filled with photos of my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where I looked,\Nmy mom was everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always keeping watch over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Jürgens recreated\Nthe storage room from his childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Jürgens as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be no link\Nbetween Mrs. Kemp and him as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jürgens's face as a child\Nwas placed over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with this one. And this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kemp didn't have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There, you will find proof\Nthat monsters are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it exactly as\Nmy friend wrote in his letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I received a letter in a white envelope\Nwith no sender or recipient on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At first,\Nhis over-familiar words irritated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I started getting\Na letter each and every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's obsessed with letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But soon enough,\NI started longing for those letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Those letters were fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that maybe\Nhe actually was a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, one day, a letter summoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It said, "Go to the storage room\Nin this residence."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The storage room in Mrs. Kemp's residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he know about my childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell into confusion\Nat Mrs. Kemp's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Mrs. Kemp my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I went up\Nto the second floor to Mrs. Kemp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is obsessed with letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That "friend" may have sent\Nletters to Mrs. Kemp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me. Look at me."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is how big the monster\Ninside me has grown."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Save me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside me\Nis about to burst out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan left me this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His friend… Johan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He really exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already way past eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Kohl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A long-haired Asian man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I know you're busy, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I analyzed what you talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you had made it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That Johan didn't exist in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he was\Na fictional character you created.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Rudy, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently researching\Na serial killer named Jürgens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one murder that didn't follow\Nhis usual modus operandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. Please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we're closing shop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The carnival has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-When I give the signal, apprehend him.\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And listen to their conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, you felt contempt towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you saw me cheating in college,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you've always felt contempt for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Kohl, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen and Tenma\Nare walking to the west exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get lost in the crowd\Ngoing home from the carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I'm someone\Nwho can't help but be seen with contempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudy, more importantly--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I hid my cheat sheet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Run. The cops have us surrounded."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look. Keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the doctor being threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's too loud around them,\Nso the audio is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait for me!\N-Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jürgens said he killed Mrs. Kemp\Nat the request of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the storage room\Nat Mrs. Kemp's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kemp didn't have any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Johan you told me about\Nand the friend Jürgens told me about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They passed the west exit.\NShould we apprehend him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Tenma might be holding a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The same words from Johan's messages
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,were at Mrs. Kemp's residence too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan used Mrs. Kemp like a parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and disposed of her when he was done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said,\Nit might be to erase his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to act pompous,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll tell you my analysis results.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but Johan can sniff out murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he steps into their solitude\Nand gains control over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't found any cases\Nin which he kills the foster parents
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that he lived off in his childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because he no longer finds\Nhis foster parents necessary at his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's another possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan finally found his ideal family,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and forced his way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is he trying to erase his past?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, did he join that family\Nfor a particular purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For some kind of purpose…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we've arrived at the bus terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Check which bus number he's riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the cars to the terminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Prepare for pursuit!\N-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought you a bus ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You could turn yourself in\Nand prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not chasing after Johan\Nto clear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, you can't possibly be planning on…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't feeling contempt towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed interesting,\Nbut the opportunity never arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, now we've finally become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But back then, you saw me cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you raising your head,\Nlooking my way, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was cheating back then too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Five buses left at roughly the same time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma.
